Clairenite GEORGES, Carine Georges Petitioners, v. IMMIGRATION AND NATURALIZATION SERVICE, Respondent. No. 97-71164. I & NS A72 849 379, A72 844 675. United States Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Argued and Submitted March 12, 1999. Decided Aug. 31, 2001.

*717Before B. FLETCHER, REINHARDT, and THOMAS, Circuit Judges.

ORDER1

Because petitioners’ status has been adjusted to that of lawful permanent residents, the petition for review is dismissed as moot.

. This disposition is not appropriate for publication and may not be cited to or by the courts of this circuit except as provided by Ninth Cir. R. 36-3.
